<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <meta name="description" content="Verified Merkle Lib – Incremental Merkle Tree, SHA-256, PrepaidPackage. Formally verified cryptography for web.">
  <title>Verified Merkle Lib · beaconchain‑us</title>
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body {
      background: radial-gradient(circle at 10% 20%, #0a0f1e, #03050a);
      font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif;
